-- Banpu's Takeover of Centennial Coal Approved by Australian Review Board
-- Tim Smith
-- 2010-09-20T22:51:21Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-20/banpu-s-takeover-of-centennial-coal-approved-by-australian-review-board.html

          
          
             Banpu Pcl received approval from
the Australian Foreign Investment Review Board for its takeover
of Centennial Coal Co. Ltd., according to a regulatory filing.  
